scenes.scene_text: The facts reflected in this story take place in Colombia, but it could happen anywhere in the Americas. Hundreds of young people die everyday in the streets of different cities in Latin America, without hope, without the right to a future. This film is a testament to a reality and at the same time a warning. Our youth are the future ... it is our duty to watch over them!
